summary: This is my character. I wanted to share it.
descriptionHtml:
UPDATE: I've added a level 1 version of her for those of you who would like to play Skyrim from the beginning with her. Enjoy!

Alice is my Ningheim Race character. I spent a long time on her face and I am quite happy with the result. I have started Dawnguard and built a house with Hearthfire. I also did not disable mods before uploading (sorry, I am new to Nexus). If there is demand for the file, I will create a new Level 1 no mods/no DLC save file. She is a level 69 character and has finished the main storyline and a few side quests. Input is always nice to hear.

The following mods are REQUIRED for her to work properly:

ApachiiSkyHair
The Ningheim Race
Brows - Ningheim Addon
More Freckles by Zhoken
RANs Hair
The Eyes of Beauty
Detailed Faces v2
No More Blocky Faces

I hope you enjoy!
author: fishcar
